description.en:
Fashion Coin (FSHN) is a Generation Z native cryptocurrency. A purely
peer-2-peer version of electronic cash, Fashion Coin provides seamless and effortless online payments - with maximum speed and limitless scale. Fashion Coin is based upon our own open blockchain platform CO:IN - CO-Creative Innovation Network.
